<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Random_variables_with_finitely_many_outcomes">Random variables with finitely many outcomes</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Expected_value&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Random variables with finitely many outcomes"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Consider a random variable <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle X}">
